{"tid":2005394,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[中國封殺香港電影人]","createTime":"2020-05-07T05:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T06:33:46.000Z","uid":286309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0aae6bf1c79a15d1c9baafc2b61af722b0dd4958","tid":2005394,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T05:37:14.000Z","msg":"睇翻背景，中國咁樣做基本上係搞死所有，係所有包括奶共嘅香港演員<br />\n<br />\n中國要求台港藝人保證10年「政治正確」 違反者恐遭索賠<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/member/twdaily/article/1_1737441__1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fmember%2Ftwdaily%2Farticle%2F1_1737441__1&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdfo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=a2c8d7a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fmember%2Ftwdaily%2Farticle%2F1_1737441__1&h=b387ecfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/member/twdaily/article/1_1737441__1</a><br />\n<br />\n現家英皇同天下一合作，2年內拍10套港產片<br />\n仲標明大部分製作都係本地<br />\n換言之，至少唔會係合拍片，搞死香港本土電影<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/96231589_10158033454595202_4197485080412684288_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=InoD5JGL8YcAX_YhUm-&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=fc7013919aeac8525be8c0c20db86cab&amp;oe=5ED8190B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F96231589_10158033454595202_4197485080412684288_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DInoD5JGL8YcAX_YhUm-%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Dfc7013919aeac8525be8c0c20db86cab%26oe%3D5ED8190B&h=a9377ae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n問題嚟啦<br />\n究竟係真心想搞好香港電影而合作<br />\n定只係因為中國唔會再有資本同香港電影合作<br />\n所以重投本地市場</span>"},{"pid":"0ad2f42fd1f4038e17610641eb29147b45d56cf4","tid":2005394,"uid":246962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0aae6bf1c79a15d1c9baafc2b61af722b0dd4958","tid":2005394,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci